              "coded_information": [
                "SPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The LOHENGRIN spectrometer is a parabola mass",
                "spectrometer for separation of the ionized fission",
                "fragments with the same mass over ionic charge and",
                "kinetic energy over ionic charge. A second magnetic",
                "field refocuses ions with different kinetic energies",
                "and deflects them towards an array of detectors."
              ]
            },
